description.narrative: This Activity responds to requests from the Government of Tonga for New Zealand and Australian support to build a new Fale Alea (Parliament House) and Office of the Legislative Assembly (OLA). Tropical Cyclone Gita in February 2018 destroyed the previous Fale Alea and resulted in the OLA being condemned.
